OL,3,CFootball manager 'bullied' by club,
OL,4,Cwife tells pre-inquest hearing
OL,6,FThe wife of the former Liverpool
OL,7,Fwomen's manager has told a pre-inquest
OL,8,Freview she felt he was "bullied" by
OL,9,FBurnley FC before his death.
OL,11,FMatt Beard, 47, died on September 20
OL,12,Flast year after resigning from his job
OL,13,Fas head coach of Burnley FC Women in
OL,14,FAugust, a hearing was told on Thursday.
OL,16,FMr Beard previously managed Millwall,
OL,17,FChelsea and West Ham's women's teams
OL,18,Fas well as seeing success with
OL,19,FLiverpool Women, where he won back-to-
OL,20,Fback Women's Super League titles in
OL,21,F2013 and 2014.
OL,26,@pD@XOUpD@`O]
