PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778193332
OL,3,CFootball manager 'bullied' by club,
OL,4,Cwife tells pre-inquest hearing
OL,6,FThe father-of-two, who lived in
OL,7,FHawarden, Deeside, North Wales, died
OL,8,Fat the Countess of Chester Hospital,
OL,9,Fthe hearing was told.
OL,11,FThe review at Ruthin County Hall heard
OL,12,Fhis family had concerns in relation to
OL,13,FMr Beard's time working at Burnley FC,
OL,14,Fwhich he joined after leaving
OL,15,FLiverpool in February 2025.
OL,17,FThe family felt leaving Burnley "was
OL,18,Fthe catalyst for a decline in his
OL,19,Fmental health", the hearing was told.
OL,26,@yD@aOU{D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
