PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778193332
OL,3,CFootball manager 'bullied' by club,
OL,4,Cwife tells pre-inquest hearing
OL,6,FHis wife Debbie Beard said: "Matt left
OL,7,FBurnley not to go to another job, he
OL,8,Fleft Burnley because he wasn't happy
OL,9,Fthere. Basically, they didn't allow
OL,10,Fhim to move on. I feel like they
OL,11,Fbullied him, to be honest."
OL,13,FSenior coroner John Gittins said he
OL,14,Fwould invite Burnley FC to become an
OL,15,Finterested person in the proceedings.
OL,17,FHe said anyone who may, by act or
OL,18,Fomission, have caused or contributed
OL,19,Fto a death was entitled to interested
OL,20,Fperson status.
OL,26,@nD@]OUsD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
