PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778193332
OL,3,CFootball manager 'bullied' by club,
OL,4,Cwife tells pre-inquest hearing
OL,6,FThe coroner said he would be making
OL,7,Fenquiries for further evidence from
OL,8,Ffootball agent Curtis Dawes and the
OL,9,FLeague Managers Association (LMA), who
OL,10,FMr Beard was said to have consulted
OL,11,Fbecause of concerns about his
OL,12,Ftreatment at Burnley.
OL,14,FMr Beard's stepson Scott Beard told
OL,15,Fthe inquest review he also had
OL,16,Fconcerns about the timing of social
OL,17,Fmedia posts which were "quite
OL,18,Fdamaging" to the manager.
OL,20,FThe inquest was adjourned to a later
OL,21,Fdate.
OL,26,@yD@XOUzD@IO]
