OL,3,CFootball manager 'bullied' by club,
OL,4,Cwife tells pre-inquest hearing
OL,6,FMr Beard's funeral, held at Liverpool
OL,7,FMetropolitan Cathedral, was attended
OL,8,Fby around 600 people including former
OL,9,FLiverpool player Ian Rush, and former
OL,10,FEngland internationals Casey Stoney,
OL,11,FLianne Sanderson and Fara Williams.
OL,13,FA spokesman for Burnley FC said:
OL,14,F"Burnley FC is aware of an ongoing
OL,15,Flegal process and will not be making
OL,16,Fany comment at this time."
OL,26,@vD@AOUxD@ZO]
